OL,3,CStorm Bert forces train operator to
OL,4,Ccancel their journeys
OL,6,FPassengers are being offered the
OL,7,Foption to change their travel times
OL,8,Fafter Storm Bert forces a train
OL,9,Foperator to cancel their journeys.
OL,11,FTransPennine Express has cancelled
OL,12,Ftrain services running north of
OL,13,FCarlisle with Storm Bert expecting to
OL,14,Fbring heavy snow, wind and rain in
OL,15,Fsouthern Scotland and Cumbria.
OL,17,FCustomers who already have bought
OL,18,Ftickets can change their travel plans
OL,19,Facross the next few days, until 24
OL,20,FNovember 2024.
