OL,3,CStorm Bert forces train operator to
OL,4,Ccancel their journeys
OL,6,FAdam Fairclough, Interim Customer
OL,7,FExperience and Transformation
OL,8,FDirector, said: "Due to bad weather
OL,9,Fover the weekend we have been forced
OL,10,Fto cancel some of our services on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,F"We want to keep our customers on the
OL,14,Fmove during cold weather conditions,
OL,15,Fwhich is why we have teamed up with
OL,16,Fother operators and given passengers
OL,17,Fthe option to change their plans to
OL,18,Ftravel with us.
