OL,3,CStorm Bert forces train operator to
OL,4,Ccancel their journeys
OL,6,F"We urge anyone planning to use our
OL,7,Fservices to check before they travel
OL,8,Fin case of any disruption during Storm
OL,9,FBert."
OL,11,FJason Kelly, a Met Office Chief
OL,12,FMeteorologist, says Storm Bert will
OL,13,Fstart to impact Scotland and northern
OL,14,FEngland on the morning of 23 November
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FHe said: "Warnings are in place,
OL,18,Fincluding an amber warning for snow
OL,19,Fand ice for parts of Scotland.
