OL,3,CStorm Bert forces train operator to
OL,4,Ccancel their journeys
OL,6,F"Heavy rainfall will affect much of
OL,7,Fthe UK this weekend. Rain is expected
OL,8,Fto develop during Saturday morning
OL,9,Facross southwest and southern England,
OL,10,Fbecoming particularly heavy and
OL,11,Fpersistent overnight and into Sunday.
OL,13,F"Accumulations of 50-75mm are expected
OL,14,Fto fall fairly widely during this
OL,15,Ftime. There is a chance that some
OL,16,Fplaces over Dartmoor for example,
OL,17,Fcould see 100-150 mm. In addition,
OL,18,Frapid melting of lying snow over the
OL,19,Fweekend may bring flooding for some."
