OL,3,CStorm Bert forces train operator to
OL,4,Ccancel their journeys
OL,6,FScotRail have encouraged passengers to
OL,7,Fcheck their website or travel app
OL,8,Fbefore traveling.
OL,10,FThey said: "If you're travelling this
OL,11,Fweekend, please be aware that the Met
OL,12,FOffice have issued yellow and amber
OL,13,Fweather warnings for snow, ice, wind
OL,14,Fand rain.
OL,16,F"Speed restrictions will be in place,
OL,17,Fand we've had to revise some services."
